description: Available at: https://openstudionetwork.com/keezer - Geoffrey explains how to make Chick Corea-like effects on the piano that sound wildly complicated, but are in fact easy and fun to play! Using a simple approach that works over any chord or groove, these sound effects will add variety and a little "avant garde" spice to your improvisation.  (Level: Intermediate/Adv.)
